A customer was left bruised and battered after asking a prostitute if he could pay for sex with a boiled egg.Moses Mushonga, 28, was hit around the head with a beer bottle after he offered to pay for sex with a boiled egg in the town of Mvurwi in Mashonaland province.According to dailymail.co.uk, Mushonga manhandled the woman leaning into her bra and touching her breast. But that did not sit well with the 23-year-old, Chipo,to add insult Mushonga then tried to negotiate with his only asset he had which was a boiled egg.Mushonga told Chipo that he had just spent his last bit of money on buying two boiled eggs, which costing 0.25 Zimbabwe dollars (R 3.56).Feeling disrespected and insulted Chipo hit Mushonga with a beer bottle before knocking Mushonga out.Speaking top the police Chipo stated that she felt that he needed to be taught a lesson about respect.-TNA Reporter